hrubý a schytil ma za krk?

428
00:30:38,976 --> 00:30:41,023
Vážne? Vážne by ste to dokázali?

429
00:30:41,023 --> 00:30:43,804
A prečo nie?

430
00:30:43,804 --> 00:30:49,846
Preháňam? Mám to spraviť?
Preháňam? Mám to spraviť?

431
00:30:49,846 --> 00:30:52,980
